# This directory is CLAUDE_CONFIG_DIR. At runtime Claude writes volatile state
# AND SECRETS here -- .credentials.json, .claude.json, history.jsonl, sessions/,
# projects/, todos/, file-history/, statsig/, telemetry/, caches, etc.
#
# Whitelist strategy: ignore EVERYTHING, then un-ignore only the curated config.
# This way anything Claude dumps here in the future stays untracked by default,
# so a credential or transcript can never be committed by accident.
*
!.gitignore
!README.md
!settings.json
!before-relaunch.sh
!hooks/
!hooks/*
